summary: It's a replace mod for who want to equip Exotic Weapon for your Character.
descriptionHtml:
Hey there I'm Martin"Ram"Wu,I'm a Skyrim fan from Taiwan.
Few days ago,I find a standalone Chilanum dagger mod from a India website.for some how,that website doesn't show the download link.
So, I ask my friend Huan-Sheng modeling this dagger,and i bought a steak for him as payment.
Then I import it to NifSkope to create this replace mod for fun,Huan-Sheng even  print it by 3D printer.
If you interested, just take and have fun!
author: MartinRamWu
